## Rules

- Work ONLY on the frontend.
- Do not modify backend code.
- Do not create APIs.
- Do not modify business logic.
- Preserve all existing functionality.
- Refactor only when it improves scalability.
- Use production-grade frontend architecture.
- Make the project easier for future developers to maintain.

The final result should be a clean, scalable, modern React frontend ready for continued development.